subsection.def:
equipment
                    (設備), in relation to a gas vehicle, includes
                fittings and accessories;

fill
                    (注入), in relation to a container, includes
                refill;

label
                    (標籤) means a label issued under
                    regulation 34;

permit
                    (許可證) means a permit issued under
                    regulation 26 in respect of a gas vehicle;

use
                    (使用), in relation to a motor vehicle,
                includes drive;

paragraph.content:
2 copies of all such plans as are specified in the notice, being plans in
                    addition to those specified under subregulation (2)(b)(iii);
                    or

any pressure-regulators or auxiliary systems used in connection with the
                    installation are protected from any dust or debris carried by the gas supplied
                    through the installation;

subparagraph.content:
the ingress of surface water is prevented or, if
                                                not prevented, will not damage the installation;
                                                and
